//
// This file contains the rules for determining which index template is used to initialize a project index.
//
// The rules are searched in order for the first one that matches (so more specific project types should come first).
//
// The index files of the given name can be put in "~/Library/Application Support/Apple/Developer Tools/Index Templates"
// or "/Library/Application Support/Apple/Developer Tools/Index Templates". The files should be called "<name>.pbxindex".
//
// Index templates can be turned on with "defaults write com.apple.Xcode PBXCodeSenseEnableIndexTemplates YES"
//
